                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#1va">ff. 1va-2</locus>
                           <desc>vb: Unidentified hymn in praise of God and other saints.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="1va">1va</locus>: በዘዚአሁ፡ አርአያወ፡ አምሳል፡ ይትአኰት፡ ወይሴባሕ፡ ስሙ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡…</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           Walatta Mikāʾel mentioned in the supplication formula at the end of the text was probably linked to the first owner of the Ms. (?) Walda Śǝllāse (s. Additio 3 and the supplication on <locus target="35ra">35ra-</locus>
                           <note>rb).
                        </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#31va">f. 31va</locus>
                           <desc>: Note listing the names: King Yoḥannǝs (r. 1872-89), Metropolitan ʾAtnatewos (in tenure 1869-76), śätätot (?) Giyorgis, priest (qasis ) Fāsiladas, and </desc>qes gabaz Kidāna Māryām.<quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="31va">31va</locus>: ንጉሥነ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ጳጳስነ፡ አትና፡ ቴዎስ፡ ሠተቶት፡ ጊዎርጊስ[sic]፡ ወለቀሲ[ስ]ሒ፡ ፋሲለደስ፡ ወለ{ቄስ}፡ ገበዝሒ፡ ኪዳነ፡ ማርያም፡</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           Written in the same hand as that of the note written on <locus target="1r">1r</locus>
                           <note> (s. Varia). It is unclear why the names were listed.
                        </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#31va">f. 31va</locus>
                           <desc>-vb: Ownership note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="31va">31va</locus>: ለዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘተሣየጦ፡ በወርቁ፡ ወልደ፡ ሠላሴ፡ ወብእሲቱ፡ ፍሥሐ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ወወለቱ፡ ወለተ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ከመ፡ ይኵኖሙ፡ መርሐ፡ በመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፡ ዘሠረቆ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡ በሥልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ፡ ውጉዘ፡ [<locus target="31vb">31vb</locus>] ለይኵን።</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note>
                           The note mentions the Ms. was bought by Walda Śǝllāse (his wife is Fǝśśǝḥa Giyorgis, his daughter is Walatta Mikāʾel).
                        </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus target="#31vb">f. 31vb</locus>
                           <desc>: Ownership note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="31vb">31vb</locus>: ለዘቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘተሳየጦ፡ ገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወለተ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ገብረ፡ አምላክ፡ ወለተ፡ መድኅን። ወለደ፡ አናንያ፡ ኪዳነ፡ ማርያም።</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note>
                           The note mentions that Gabra ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer and other individuals bought the Ms.
                        </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Short note ገብረ፡ ጊዎርጊስ፡ ወለዲያቆንሒ written in the same hand that of Additio 2: <locus target="1r">1r</locus>.&#xD;
- Doodles: <locus target="35v">35v</locus>.</item>
